outside the ghetto
of hardcore rock fans.

187
00:13:28,547 --> 00:13:30,871
This is Kiss.
Each sold separately.

188
00:13:30,971 --> 00:13:33,823
And you can put them
in any crazy pose you want.

189
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:39,012
